Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是她真正的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝去吧 到銀河的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你們為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌和Vajra都是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Quarter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來晚了 奧茲馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有點私事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲馬少校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我隊長 SK-3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為粉碎Galaxy的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為粉碎格蕾絲·奧克娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及和她勾結的人的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他們和他們同夥的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼根據信口雌黃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據我有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是SK-4的識別信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了 他的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破那障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被Vajra擊沉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三島總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後詳細聽你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括暗殺葛拉斯總統一事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統不是被Vajra所殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理準備 雷昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被揭穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些年輕人還真行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無傷大雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓他們做個好夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 Battle Galaxy發射出眾多熱源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost V9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V9？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3向SK-4通話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到就回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡 葛蘭上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接收 阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-4向Battle Frontier通話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定會救出蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 借你的力量一用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的歌 讓她睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 用你的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時 我聽見了你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了你心靈的呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無心插柳柳成蔭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心栽花花不開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨心所想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要 飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機跟上 突擊LOVE HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾 賜予我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 路哈尼 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在解除你們的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾讓Macross City陷入恐懼深淵的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶大系統解除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的聲音 謝麗爾的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找回你真正的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈的空間波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前天壤地別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間波急速展開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逐漸構築網絡構造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 Vajra的行動…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy 到底幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到 感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是星座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不再需要Little Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們獲得了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽令 螻蟻們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在獲得了整個宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始文明也對這份力量懼怕 憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於進化為超時空生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助Vajra的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是格蕾絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大個兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無效？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 次元斷層？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對與Queen直接接通的我們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪倒在我們能支配命運的神明之力下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛 我的耳朵 我的手足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著強韌的利爪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Macross 11
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}行星 Eden
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}地球 Macross City
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識我們的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌 阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧中彈 總算擺脫了他們的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱吧 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷憤怒與歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓所有情緒乘著歌放飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這次一定要阻止這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們兄妹的贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌把Vajra…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra在蘭歌的歌聲影響下停止了攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是與我們為敵了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是與Vajra Queen的空間波旗鼓相當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔓延開來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 謝麗爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 我的工作結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來 謝麗爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有謝麗爾小姐我才展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為謝麗爾小姐給他力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多也才能飛上天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過吧 絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來吧 謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們再飛一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告戰場上的所有將士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra並非我們真正的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佔據Vajra女王的格蕾絲·奧格娜等人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是我們真正的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對自己的翅膀懷有一份自豪感的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們共同前行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUND WAVE 坐標確認
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦點護罩集中於主炮前端
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 無謂的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直奔主島而來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護了我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲傳達到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和謝麗爾小姐的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Varja也有自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和我們大不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們無法理解人類為何這麼零零散散
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各做各的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以Vajra想把能用空間波交流的我\N從不明底細的人類手中救出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它們自從感知到謝麗爾小姐不同與我的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白我們每個人都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不通過交流無法互相理解的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家擁抱吧 直到銀河盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的網絡協議傳達不到？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是歌的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷層護罩 再次展開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才能突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通道 Vajra們在斷層上打開了通道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍跟上Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮損傷 發射不能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在 Macross Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托付給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人類進化的究極形態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼進化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿Vajra做犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掩護你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:19:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多 瞄準女王頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭部？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的心靈並非頭部而在腹部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra是用肚子歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些螻蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你們連接在一起深有體會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論到哪裏人都是孤獨的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正因為孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會愛他人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Vajra的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Vajra是無須交流的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌到底是用來做什麼的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra數萬年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 數億年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與居住在其他銀河的群落相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交配時互相呼喚的情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛啊 愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾和蘭歌為我們打開的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.83,0:24:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻氣全飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論歌還是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.00,0:24:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.75,0:24:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.47,0:24:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏開始
